subject: Basketball
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: The Rutgers women’s basketball team was hoping for a victory, a fresh start and some good news as it opened its season Sunday night. It got none of the above, losing 60-58 to No. 7 Stanford.
